Title: Pipeline
Description: A tender process has been proposed or a potential tender is being explored. There is no guarantee that this process will proceed.

Title: Planned
Description: A tender process is planned but is not yet taking place.

Title: Active
Description: A tender process is currently taking place.

Title: Cancelled
Description: The tender process has been cancelled.

Title: Withdrawn
Description: This tender process has been withdrawn. This may be due to a decision not to proceed with a full tender process after the pipeline or planning stage, or may be because subsequent contracting stages will no longer be managed through this particular information system.
